snippet.title: Regular Show: Mordecai and Rigby in 8-bit Land - 3DS - Best Regular Show game ever! (Trailer)
snippet.description:
THIS is the BEST Regular Show game ever! Yes it's also the first and only...but hey, there's always a start!
Regular Show: Mordecai and Rigby in 8-bit land releases today on Nintendo 3DS and the buds need you help to get out from the weird video games they have been transported in.

For more information, please visit your local Namco Bandai Games website, http://www.namcobandaigames.eu

Talk about this game, share tips & win goodies at http://www.namcobandaigames.eu/community
